title: Marital Conflict and Gottman's Four Horsemen
description:
Dr. Kirk Honda talks with Lesli Doares from Happily Ever After Is Just The Beginning about marital conflict and Gottman's four horsemen that predict divorce.

 

The Psychology In Seattle Podcast.

 

April 20, 2018.

 

Email: Contact@PsychologyInSeattle.com
